# ğŸª¨ Iberpiedra Buscador

Iberpiedra Buscador is a full-stack web application developed for internal use in a family-owned company.  
The application allows managing a stone products catalog through a web interface, providing full CRUD functionality.

This project is part of my personal portfolio and represents my **first complete independently developed application**, covering frontend development, backend API design, database integration, deployment, and production configuration.

